    <title>依据圣经作决择系列10-存在动机的角度:选择良善</title>
    <link href="http://mengfu.org/2022/yi-ju-sheng-jing-zuo-jue-ze-xi-lie-10-cun-zai-dong-ji-de-jiao-du-xuan-ze-liang-shan.html"/>
