    <title>依据圣经作决择系列7-情况处境的角度:了解事实真相</title>
    <link href="http://mengfu.org/2022/yi-ju-sheng-jing-zuo-jue-ze-xi-lie-7-qing-kuang-chu-jing-de-jiao-du-liao-jie-shi-shi-zhen-xiang.html"/>
